            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 6800,
            "LocalizeKR": "이대로 얼굴에\n잔뜩 칠해버려야지!",
            "LocalizeJP": "お顔全体に、\nくまなく塗ってあげるねっ！",
